{"questionId":"25678","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The following diagram shows part of the graph of a quadratic function <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi></math>.</p>\n<p>The graph of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi></math> has its vertex at <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>)</mo></math>, and it passes through point <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>Q</mtext></math> as shown.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/bb9b6d38abbe948917fcba47938cccb8f876b389.png\"></p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The function can be written in the form <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>h</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>k</mi></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Write down the values of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>h</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>k</mi></math>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp;(accept&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><msup><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn></math>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"25678","referenceCode":"22M.1.SL.TZ2.7b.i","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Write down the values of h and k.","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"b.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.6—Quadratic function"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}